## ğŸ§  Key Learnings
- How network traffic analysis reveals sensitive information
- Risks of transmitting data in clear text
- Importance of encryption in modern networks

---

## ğŸ” Remediation Recommendations
- Encrypt data in transit (HTTPS, TLS)
- Encrypt sensitive data at rest
- Implement strict access controls (ACLs / RBAC)
- Monitor network traffic for anomalies

